images.prompt: In a dimly lit, angled room suffused with the eerie glow of a solar flare, a wire lich witch looms ominously, her form intricately woven from shimmering strands of metallic ochre and grey steel, while delicate crystal webs stretch across the walls, refracting the harsh light into haunting patterns that dance across the surfaces, creating an unsettling yet mesmerizing atmosphere that blends elements of sci-fi horror with a surreal elegance, inviting the viewer to explore the depths of this otherworldly realm where the boundaries of reality and nightmare intertwine.
